      "text": "Last edit over 4 years ago by green.daisy\n2\nNeeds Review\n2\ni or: another psyche (\"Thomas\") operated my body - in '71 + again in 3-74 when we con habitated. This is a supernatural self, nicht ich He put the Acts material in \"Tears\" - why? message to trigger himself into being in 2-74? I was taken over not just in 2-3-74 but in There were 2 me's, as Hal guessed. One of 171 them supernatural + part of a conspiracy, making use of me. Somehow connected with the Xerox missive. It didn't call him forth",
